msgstr ""
"Eine verwandte Ressource, die eine Version, Edition oder Anpassung der "
"beschriebenen Ressource ist."

msgid "Instructional Method"
msgstr "Lehrmethode"

msgid ""
"A related resource that is substantially the same as the described "
